FALL GIVE-A-YAY! CLOSED
Baking season is back!! To make sure you’re all geared up, I’ve teamed up with my favorite baking friends to bring one of you the chance to w.i.n. your own new KITCHEN AID MIXER no matter where you are in the world!
To enter, follow my friends here:

2- L.I.K.E. And S.A.V.E. my post 
3- T.a.g. 3 baking friends. The more the higher your chances! 
4. Don’t forget to tell me your favorite fall bake! 
For 10 extra entries, share on your stories! 
Open w.o.r.l.d.w.i.d.e. Starts now and ends 16 SEP 12 noon CST. W.i.n.n.e.r. will be announce by 18 SEP! Not affiliated with Facebook Inc. 
Please note I will never ask you for to click any link if you w.i.n. The winner will be announced on my page so do not open any links from pages not mentioned in this post
